The Lychee Martini Drink Cocktail BombTM. Perfect for the mysterious Bond Girl—sweet lychee brightens up the dry martini with its alluring and sensual aroma. Try it shaken or stirred with your favorite vodka.

Can be used for mocktails, does not contain alcohol. Makes 1 or 2 drinks.

How to Use:

Add to sparkling water.
Add your favorite alcohol.
Add ice, shake or blend.
Garnish. Cheers!
